    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3096520/extras/3ac5cd523828050c14986f9bbcdf8f5a.poster.avif?t=1768652425\" width=600 height=62 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3096520/extras/3ac5cd523828050c14986f9bbcdf8f5a.webm?t=1768652425\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3096520/extras/3ac5cd523828050c14986f9bbcdf8f5a.mp4?t=1768652425\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >About the game:</h2><br>The most wicked of evil spirits has returned to curse the world. Explore the land of Aestlanda as the Quiet One, a hero marked by silence on a quest to banish the wicked One Who Speaks Worm Tongue. Collect unique weapons and upgrades on your quest through undead infested dungeons, haunted woods, and corrupted cities while you face ever-stronger enemies and mighty bosses.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3096520/extras/a7f0f94d150763bca701a3350338665c.webp?t=1768652425\" width=612 height=41 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features:</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 14 levels filled with weapons, upgrades, and secrets. <br></li><li> 7 unique Bosses to conquer.<br></li><li>Many unique enemies that will challenge your skill.<br></li><li> 3 possible Endings.<br></li><li> Side stories and lore galore, for you to explore!</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3096520/extras/2cb3b22682494cb6c3aea4963200a775.webp?t=1768652425\" width=612 height=41 /></span>",
